WEBVTT

00:00:28.883 --> 00:00:34.007
i to je ultimativna prilika biti svoj,

00:00:34.031 --> 00:00:35.746
jer ne možeš biti ništa drugo.

00:00:35.770 --> 00:00:38.577
Pred svojim kolegama na brodu si ogoljen.

00:00:38.601 --> 00:00:40.025
To je mali prostor.

00:00:40.049 --> 00:00:42.284
Maiden je jedrilica dugačka 18 metara.

00:00:42.308 --> 00:00:44.707
12 žena se nalazi na tom
brodu od 18 metara.

00:00:44.731 --> 00:00:47.475
Doslovce ste jedna uz drugu,

00:00:47.499 --> 00:00:49.955
tako da morate biti svoji.

00:00:49.979 --> 00:00:53.254
Najveći trenutak za mene kada jedrim

00:00:53.278 --> 00:00:56.317
je trenutak kada kopno nestane.

00:00:56.341 --> 00:00:59.185
To je neopisiv trenutak...

00:00:59.209 --> 00:01:00.303
(uzdah)